          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Urges Laos to cease its assaults on the Hmong community, respect the Convention on the Rights of the Child, and uphold its commitments to human rights treaties. </p> <p>Urges the United Nations to condemn the actions of Laos and invoke the Responsibility to Protect mechanisms. </p>]]></text>
